    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h2 id="how_wishlu_works">
            how does wishlu work?
        </h2>
        <div class="col_12">
            <h4>Here is how you use wishlu.com:</h4>
            <div class="col_12">
                <h5>Create wishlus.</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>wishlus</b> are unique lists of anything you want from anywhere for any occasion. You create them and name them and organize them any way you please.</li>
                    <li>You can add as many items (wishes) as you want to one, some, or all of your wishlus, plus images, notes, cost, and location to make buying the perfect thing for you easy and fun.</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>Create wishloops.</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>wishloops</b> are personalized and private circles of family & friends whom you invite to join you on wishlu.</li>
                    <li>Just like wishlus, you can create unique wishloops and name them and organize them any way you want.</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>Share your wishlus with your wishloops.</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Share your wishlus with selected wishloops so that members can view all of the important details about your wishes and buy (grant) them. Or, keep a wishlu private if you just want to keep track of future gift ideas—either for yourself or for someone else.</li>
                    <li>Much like traditional gift registries, wishlu keeps track of who is buying what so that multiples of one item are not purchased; however, wishlu is unique in that it keeps everything a secret until a date selected by the person buying an item—just like traditional gift giving.</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>Update your wishlu profile.</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fill out <b>a few of my favorite things</b> to let your family & friends know your favorite everything: colors, perfume, sports teams, musicians, flowers etc. Doing so makes buying you a thoughtful anytime gift even easier.</li>
                    <li>Provide your clothing sizes in stats and your shipping address, too.</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>On your iPhone</h5>
                <h6>(free mobile apps for your ANdroid and iPad are coming soon.):</h6>
                <ul>
                    Just like wishlu.com, the free wishlu app for your iPhone lets you create unique wishlus and wishloops with your smartphone. Capture all of the important information about the things you want just by scanning items’ barcodes when you are out and about and then share the details with your wishloops, including images, notes, cost, and location.
                </ul>
                <h6>
                    Creating wishlus and wishloops is just the start.  We have an entire portfolio of smart and fun features on their way, and we can’t wait to share them with you. Be sure to stay on the lookout for correspondence from us about updates and quick tutorials to make the most of out of what you can do with wishlu.
                </h6>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h3 id="how_do_i_get_started">
            how do I get started?
        </h3>
        <div class="col_12">
            <h4>get started in a few simple steps.</h4>
            <div class="col_12">
                <h5 style="text-decoration: underline;">
                    Add an item to your birthday wishlu.
                </h5>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        Select “add a new item” on the home page and enter the name of an item you would like to receive as a birthday gift in the search bar, such as “Hunter boots.”
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Click “view” on the item that best matches what you want in the search results.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Enter any details about the item you would like your friends to know, such as the size of the item you need or the color you would like by clicking the “notes” tab.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Click “add to a wishlu” and using the down arrow select your birthday wishlu.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Return to the home page by clicking on the wishlu “w” icon in the upper left hand corner and repeat the steps above as many times as you like to continue adding items to your birthday wishlu.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="col_12">
                <h5 style="text-decoration: underline;">
                    Invite people to view your birthday wishlu.
                </h5>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click your name in the upper right hand corner of any page and select the “invite” link on the dropdown menu.</li>
                    <li>Enter the email addresses of people you would like to invite to view your wishlu and click “invite,” or select “invite whoever’s missing” to send requests to your Facebook friends to join you on wishlu.</li>
                    <li>When friends accept your invitation, you will be notified and they will automatically be placed in your friends wishloop.</li>
                    <li>By default, people who belong to your friends wishloop can see your birthday wishlu.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="col_12">
                <h5 style="text-decoration: underline;">Create your profile.</h5>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click your name in the upper right hand corner of any page and select the “profile” link on the dropdown menu.</li>
                    <li>Click the “edit profile” button in the upper right hand corner of the profile page.</li>
                    <li>Click the camera icon to upload a profile picture.</li>
                    <li>List your favorite things in the text box below “a few of my favorite things” to give people some ideas about the kinds of items that always make much appreciated gifts for you: your favorite fragrance, band, author, candy, team, restaurant, flowers, wine etc. Click the disk icon to save.</li>
                    <li>Enter your sizes under stats to help people when they are shopping for clothing for you. By default, your friends wishloop can see this information, but you can change who sees your stats via the privacy setting next to each dropdown.</li>
                    <li>Click the “stores and brands I like” to let people know the best places to shop for you.</li>
                    <li>Enter your shipping address for easy reference for your friends if they would like to send you a gift. By default, your address is private, but you can change who sees your stat via the privacy setting.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <h6>Click the <i class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle"></i> buttons wherever you see them for quick tips.</h6>
            <h6>To receive notifications when one of your friends adds an item to his or her wishlu, click the feed icon in the upper right corner of his or her wishlu.</h6>
        </div>
    </div>

