    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h3 id="how_do_i_bookmark">
            how do I add an item to wishlu that is not appearing in my search results by using the wishlu bookmarklet tool?
        </h3>
        <span>The wishlu bookmarklet tool lets you add an item from any product page on the web.</span>
        <ol>
            <li>Click the “bookmarklet” link on the dropdown menu under your name in the upper right hand corner of the page.</li>
            <li>Drag and drop the “add to wishlu” icon to your browser.</li>
            <li>Any time you want to add an item from a product page on the web, make a note of its price, click on the icon in your browser, and select the image of the item you want.</li>
            <li>Enter any details about the item you would like your friends to know, such as the size of the item you need or the color you would like by clicking the “notes” tab.</li>
            <li>If you would like to add the item to an existing wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and using the down arrow select the wishlu to which you would like to add the item.  If you would like to add the item to a new wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and then type the name of your new wishlu in the text box. Save the information by clicking “add.”</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h3 id="how_do_i_search">
            how do I search online for an item to add to wishlu?
        </h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Click the green plus sign icon at the top of the page or select the “add a new item” button in the center of the dashboard, which you can access via the wishlu “w” icon in the upper left hand corner of a page.</li>
            <li>Enter the name of the item you would like to add in the search bar. You can search the products of our retail partners here by store, website, brand, or product name.</li>
            <li>If you would like to add an item to your “just me” wishlu, click “save” on the item that best matches what you want in the search results, or click “view” to add the item to an existing or new wishlu that you can share with others.</li>
            <li>Enter any details about the item you would like your friends to know, such as the size of the item you need or the color you would like by clicking the “notes” tab.</li>
            <li>If you would like to add the item to an existing wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and using the down arrow select the wishlu to which you would like to add the item.  If you would like to add the item to a new wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and then type the name of your new wishlu in the text box. Save the information by clicking “add.”</li>
            <li>Return to the home page by clicking on the “w” icon in the upper left hand corner and repeat the steps above as many times as you like to continue adding items to an existing or new wishlu.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h3 id="how_do_i_add_custom">
            how do I add an item to wishlu that I can’t find online?
        </h3>
        <span>Some items you may want to add to wishlu can’t be found online. Say, for instance, you want to add an item you saw at a boutique that doesn’t have product pages online for all of its items. You can manually add information about the item to wishlu.</span>
        <ol>
            <li>Click the green plus sign icon at the top of a page or select the “add a new item” button in the center of the home page.</li>
            <li>Click the “add item manually” button on the next page.</li>
            <li>First, enter the name of the item.</li>
            <li>Next, click on the camera icon to upload a photo from your library and enter any other details you want about the item.</li>
            <li>If you would like to add the item to an existing wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and using the down arrow select the wishlu to which you would like to add the item.  If you would like to add the item to a new wishlu, click “add to a wishlu” and then type the name of your new wishlu in the text box. Save the information by clicking “add.”</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="col_12" style="border: 2px solid lightblue; background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding:10px;">
        <h3 id="how_do_i_wishlu">
            how do I create a new wishlu?
        </h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Select “my wishlus” on the home page or via the “wishlus” link on the dropdown menu under your name in the upper right hand corner of any page and then click the “create a new wishlu” button.</li>
            <li>Enter the name of your new wishlu in the text box, such as “graduation.”</li>
            <li>If you would like, select a color for your new wishlu and choose a date that is associated with your wishlu. For example, if your graduation party is on June 7, you may want to link this date to your new graduation wishlu. Whenever you choose a date to associate with a wishlu, friends who have permission to view the wishlu will be reminded of the upcoming date and prompted to view the wishlu linked to it.</li>
            <li>Determine whether you want your new wishlu to be visible to everyone (public), some of your wishloops or individual friends (shared) or, for now, only you (private). By default your friends wishloop can see your new wishlu unless you deselect it under “wishloops” via “shared.”</li>
            <li>If you decide you want to share your wishlu, you can choose to share the wishlu with whichever wishloops you like by selecting “wishloops” under “who can see this wishlu?” or you can share your wishlu with individual wishlu friends by selecting “friends” under “who can see this wishlu?”</li>
        </ol>
        <h5>For more some fun wishlu ideas, click <a href="#wishlu_ideas">What are some wishlu ideas?</a></h5>
    </div>

