        <h3 id="what_is_just_me">
            what is the just me wishlu?
        </h3>
        <span>
            The “just me” wishlu is a private wishlu that only you can see. Add items to it and then sort them later or use this wishlu to keep track of future gift ideas for yourself or others.
        </span>
